Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425仅分享于伊莉论坛/动画下载区(免空)请勿任意转载
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:17.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,早上了  该起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再让我睡五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:29.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再等我体温上升五度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:33.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说米亚  你为什么会在我床上？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:37.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为太冷了体温升不上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:39.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以就想用Darling来温暖一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:42.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拉米亚族是变温动物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我去准备洗澡水  你等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:45.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想要让Darling来温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.94,0:00:56.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling的体温传过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:58.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,胸部！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,冷静…我要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:02.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能有邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…等…脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:06.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,静动脉完全被勒住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,暂停  米亚  这样会缺氧的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,弃权  弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  别那么粗暴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:13.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又睡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不想个办法挣脱的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:22.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:26.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一放松反而更紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,惨了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling  尾巴的尖端有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,发现弱点？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,效果拔群啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拘束渐渐变松了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:48.53,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:48.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是脖子还是紧紧地缠着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:51.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,意识快要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快点松开我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要那么用力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:10.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已经…不行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:13.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:30.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  我知道了  这就起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都怪Darling一大早就这么激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:35.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:38.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再等我五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.59,0:03:03.26,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「拉米亚的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,趁米亚还没睡第三次觉前  要让她身体暖和起来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:20.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为了让米亚寄宿房子改造了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到处都太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:28.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她是怎么上厕所的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,热水准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…刚好准…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢  Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么我先下去泡啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:47.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊~真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:49.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,日本的浴池真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我在书上看过  日本好像有叫温泉这东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好想和Darling一起去一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:03.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的  你在偷瞄什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:03.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:07.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我去准备做早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:09.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:13.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有热水了就不需要我来暖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且  我还知道  温泉里有个叫混浴的文化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.26,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…  米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以说Darling也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.73,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,背…背后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚从禁止事项来说这样不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:28.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,混浴是很不好的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,温泉里还有那么见不得人的文化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不…不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那让我体验一下混浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是为了文化交流才来日本的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.23,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,等  等  等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才不想和Darling以外的人混浴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我初体验的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊  好冷！我的体温要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  你在做什么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:06:00.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本设施不提供混浴的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是无情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,超人气组合  ANM48
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.08,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&H360AF5&\3c&HFF00FF&\pos(510,542)}兽  耳  相  伴  每  一  天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:19.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,出道以来连续更新榜首的纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作为世界上首支以亚人种组成的偶像团体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,震撼力非同小可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不止是震撼力  还有非常可爱的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:37.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,ANM48能如此活跃  多亏了三年前实施的法案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他种族间交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:47.92,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,170)\fs40\c&H9B0EC3&\3c&HFFFFFF&}他种族间交流法实施三周年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:44.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是为了长期被政府隐藏起来的非人类种族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,进行交流而制定的法案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因此  文化交流正积极推进了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:56.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所幸没有发生重大摩擦  他们也渐渐融入人类社会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.35,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过  世界没有想象那样发生了巨大变化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.66,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,是啊  我前几天还遇到了某个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,才没有那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一大早我就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:14.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,几天前我根本还没想过事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:20.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,早安  来留主公人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:25.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么了  竟然吓成这样  把我忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:29.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是他种族间交流的协调员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:32.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么你擅自进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,能也给我一份早餐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是来吃饭的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:39.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:43.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,来确认你是否违反了禁止事项
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:49.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为了文化交流而来的亚人种要是伤害他们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.42,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(385,558)}拉米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:48.34,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(364,562)}勇  者  攻  击！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.23,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\pos(442,564)}拉米亚受到58点伤害！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,会依据他种族交流法受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.26,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs56\pos(464,272)}打  败  了  拉  米  亚  ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.51,TOP,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fs56\pos(564,514)}获  得  了         4649  经  验  值  ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:58.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作为寄宿家庭方  怕你对法案无知所以才来确认的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么无知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:03.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,本来就是墨须小姐搞错了才把米亚带来我家的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我家又不是寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没有这段记忆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太随意了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你这也能算他种族间交流协调员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这个暂且不说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还暂且不说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:20.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然米亚说这里好  那你就需要好好学习才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:23.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你父母在国外工作真是刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哪有这样自说自话的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再来杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:27.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好~好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才没有伤害她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:35.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,也有那方面含意的伤害哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她也有正常的生殖器  要做的话也能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没有被紧逼过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,毕竟她们可是很热情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,代表种族而来的女孩子的纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:54.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人类要是玷污她  就变成外交问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果你要是越过了那条线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就会依法将你逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:06.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:06.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她则会被遣返回国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虽然很可怜  但这就是规定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么  Sex了没？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎  没有…绝对没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是有稍微考虑过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她下半身虽然是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是身材火辣  胸部也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:27.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且又是个美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最重要的是十分迷恋你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你很容易屈服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:35.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂！你在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:44.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果对Darling出手  就算是墨须小姐也不能原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看来他也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:50.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~开个玩笑  玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且我这就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:58.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling君  请务必切记不要触犯禁止事项喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个  米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:11.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你不把身体擦干的话身体又会冷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:15.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个禁止事项就那么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个时候  我第一次来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:23.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为我们拉米亚族下半身是蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,第一次见到的人一般肯定会感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:30.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我很不安你是否会接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是Darling你用笑容迎接了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这让我非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最近的电视上也经常看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以没有那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:07.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和禁止事项没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:11.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为只要是Darling  对我做什么也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:13.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,让我受伤我也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:16.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…米亚  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.29,0:11:24.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,留下无法磨灭的第一次痕迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:30.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,最喜欢Darling了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:34.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:37.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:39.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,禁止事项有那么重要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:45.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就快要…断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,断了！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:53.63,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:12:00.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.24,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.59,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只不过是肩膀脱臼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的是让你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:14.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.63,0:12:19.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,约会  约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天要和Darling约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,约会！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么关于约会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对社会见习的最后确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭不能让留学生单独行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,必须整天共同行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好好带她在街上逛逛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:50.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我说墨须小姐  这不是协调员的工作吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是有很多事要忙的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:56.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,绝对不能带去爱情旅馆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快走吧！Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:04.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,约会开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:33.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,印象中日本是很死板的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:35.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但没想到有那么多好玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:38.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过到处都是人类专用的设施太狭小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有点让人遗憾的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好想去唱卡拉OK呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,卡拉OK的包厢太狭窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,现在社会整体还没做到对应全种族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:50.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:55.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快看快看Darling  这间店对应全种族喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,进去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等  别拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是  内衣店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那…我在外面等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.83,0:14:06.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐不是说过要一直一起行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思  有拉米亚用的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在这边  请慢慢挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:16.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:18.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感觉好不自在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:22.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说米亚有穿内裤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:24.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是怎么穿的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  你觉得哪一件适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:31.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不怎么穿胸罩  所以不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是  我也不太懂胸罩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你试穿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,试穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等…等  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:45.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为我们不管什么时候都要在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以  Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我直接穿给你看你选一件喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:54.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想穿Darling喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想让Darling能更加喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以要仔细看好再选哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哪…哪件都很合适喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,全部都买了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.61,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,硅胶隐形胸贴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过这形状也够奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,背面是贴合的还有点热呼呼的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da…Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:23.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个  强行把你拉进试衣间是我不好  我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以把内裤还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的！Darling你这个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:34.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原来有穿啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.63,0:15:35.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:42.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling真是的  玩弄内裤只有变态才会做的事喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:46.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  那是我不知道  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:51.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过那么在意的话干脆给你看吧Darling！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哇！那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:57.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是恶心  居然叫Darling？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真恶心呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,刚刚你是故意挡住？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:12.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  想想禁止事项
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:16.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人类不能伤害他种族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是反过来也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:23.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果伤害人类的话  就会被遣返回国了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他种族居然还有这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:30.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是第一次看见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,现拉米亚族NOW！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:32.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那男的是谁  男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:35.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那…那个  等等  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:38.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,请不要随意拍照好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:42.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling  我想去没人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不引人注目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.27,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,爱情旅馆！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:53.70,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好像是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我…我要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:03.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这是紧急避难绝没有下流的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:08.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这里的浴室虽然比不上Darling家的但也很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米…米亚  你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯  稍微好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不过这里是HOTEL吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:18.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我没有做过夜的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是休息而已  不过夜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明是HOTEL却不过夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那这里是做什么的地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是做什么的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说这个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:30.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快把那个放一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:39.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然人类还是会抗拒我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:46.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,对我们温柔的人也是受法律要求才会那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:51.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling这么温柔对待我也是因为怕被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没…没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看  Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我并不可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,这样的无防备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就算Darling伤害我  我也不会反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,即使这样Darling还会害怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:26.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不许动！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们是他种族间交流法保安局的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我们得到情报有人带拉米亚族少女做出淫乱行为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我以触犯他种族间交流法名义将对你进行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:39.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊啦  Darling君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:47.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦  可别小看国家权力机关的情报收集能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛  说白了就是Twitter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:04.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,刚才的蛇女居然来爱情旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:06.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的是好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等一下  你们这些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.47,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎么那家伙能做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:12.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说回来她有OO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,别笑死人了  怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:17.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,下手太重…了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:44.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好痛！痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:47.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是男孩子吧  忍耐一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不就是稍微伤到关节而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个  对方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我跟那两个人很和气地谈了一下后他们就和解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:01.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,还有  以防万一确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:02.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你脸上的伤是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:03.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我摔倒伤到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:08.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那么  多多保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,为什么要那么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:23.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那个尾击是我自己撞上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不算什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是  我不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:32.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你想想  我出手的话就是普通打架而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:37.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要是你打了那种家伙被遣返回国就太不值了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:43.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在作为拉米亚族或其他种族前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:46.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚只是一个女孩子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:50.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是不能原谅那两个人对女孩子那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:52.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的只有这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,果然还是会变成这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:06.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling是真心把我当作一名女孩子看待的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那刚才的事  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等  好不容易躲过被遣返回国的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:16.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,没关系  这下初体验的隔阂也能消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,话说回来Darling君  今天的晚餐是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:22.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你…你在干什么啊  墨须小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:24.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,干什么  我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太自说自话了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊  让他们和解真的太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,区区咖哩不嫌弃的话请用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啦真的  怎感觉不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,难得气氛这么好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亚  你忘了这个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.85,0:21:47.24,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎啊！啊------------！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:21.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}帕皮！帕皮是哈耳庇的帕皮哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}哎  帕皮哈皮帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}是哈庇厄族的帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}不对  是帕比的帕皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:35.02,标题,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,1)\\pos(660,483)\\c&HFBD49E&}「哈耳庇厄和半人马的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:35.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H781777&\c&HA0CCF9&}没想到真遇到了  这简直是命运！
