Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.22,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:47.87,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.39,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:57.21,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster's life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.51,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其一  不要在意他人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.07,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,要大胆以及慎重地选择目标
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.61,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其二  日常问候要适度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:15.09,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,当做好心理准备的话  就上阵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:18.85,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其三  发现机会就要迅速瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.48,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,开火开火开火开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.97,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其四  不需要去顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.85,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最后确实给目标的心致命一击而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:30.56,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要有爱的话  就算只有一分也足够
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:36.78,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,比那个更重要的是  遵循欲望的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.80,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,冲吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.40,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿！亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:45.21,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,因为有你在所以才会是最强的是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.84,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果能一直在一起那就是最棒的不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.37,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,无论前方会遇到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:53.17,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要和你就 All OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.74,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如今以无庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:58.48,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这肯定就是宇宙第一的爱对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.86,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,等不及你的答案  我已经
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:07.73,OP-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速坠入爱河！
