Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:05.32,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:09.36,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,OY! OY! OY! Hey Sumisu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:11.53,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,点燃手中拥有的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.42,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无疑问的个人主义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.95,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,还记得吗随时光流逝的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.98,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,真实如同海市蜃楼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.81,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,这不是逃跑是脚停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:22.65,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,那才是我的美学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:25.30,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,规律对我自身来说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:26.98,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:31.44,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,徒劳无功(徒劳无功) 功过事迹(功过事迹)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:35.63,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,扭扭腰(扭扭腰) 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.52,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们代表正义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.80,0:22:40.36,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我们不容置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.52,0:22:44.03,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果真实是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:47.64,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！场面大话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.29,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,HEY！！我不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.30,0:22:53.10,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是稍微说一点而已...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:23:01.80,ED-CN,brume0425,0,0,0,,愿我的心能获得安宁...
